Common.Strapline.Common.Text: A BERGER WITH THE LOT – 1,549 SQM*

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Part of a well presented complex, Level 1 at 334 Cormack Road Wingfield is a terrific tenancy of 240 square metres. With good levels of natural light and being fully self contained including toilets and kitchen, the tenancy will suit the corporate tenant seeking prime space in the heart of Adelaide's industrial heartland.

Located strategically near Port Adelaide and the CBD, the location offers streamlined access via South Road to major freight routes including the Port River Expressway which leads to Highway 1 to the north-east and Port Adelaide to the north-west.

The fitout is all open plan that is flexible and able to be easily used. Eight (8) on-site park are available with the tenancy plus ample on-site carparks.
